{"type": "article", "id": 4296, "title": "Voilà Roberope 衣帽架", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-11T07:46:05Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233301nBLu0KcsNok7YD8Z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\tVoilà Roberope 是一款非常简洁的衣帽架，两位设计师 Justus Kränzle 与 Jan-Patric Metzger 仅用一根 4 米长的涤纶纱线材质的绳子做成了一个形状不规则弯曲的衣帽架，并给其搭配了一个不锈钢材质的挂钩。此外，Voilà Roberope 还具有防水特性，室内室外皆可使用，目前提供黑 、白、红、蓝以及米色 5 色可选，定价 195 美元，<a href=\"http://www.stillfried.com/collections/furniture-storage/products/roberope\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233259cz1xOGJXagF4TeqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233259uemakQCgwvLXRdzD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233259wCIKMqcBZzyfLRHQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233300I87yEKVmgepo9w3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}